# ==========================================
# CollabClass Frontend Configuration
# ==========================================

# Google OAuth Configuration
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com

# API Configuration (if needed for different environments)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# ==========================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ==========================================

# 1. Get Google OAuth Client ID:
#    - Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#    - Create OAuth 2.0 credentials (Web Application)
#    - Copy the Client ID and paste it below
#    - Ensure http://localhost:5173 is in authorized origins

# 2. Frontend runs on port 5173 (Vite default)
#    - Ensure backend is running on port 5000

# 3. After updating this file:
#    - Restart the frontend dev server: npm run dev
